Very nice and popular duck rice here, the store is very near to the bus stop, you won't miss it as there will always be a long queue.
Vegetarian options: specialty vegetarian stall, beancurd, red/green bean soup, local desserts & pancake, yong tau foo, chwee kueh, prata, yam cake, goreng pisang, fried carrot cake, bread & buns

any food ?!

Wanton Mee stall is nice!

Porridge. Roast duck rice. Chix rice. Yong tau foo. Veg bee hoon. Mushroom pork noodles

almost every stall needs to queue... be prepared!

Good must try

dessert shop at the middle place sucks

Bandung is nice!!!

#01-96 chwee kueh so attitude and little cai por
